                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The monitor",
                "detector at 19-degree were determined from elastic",
                "scattering of Be-9 from a Au-197."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The relative normalization was obtained",
                "using the fixed angle monitor detector.",
                "Absolute normalization was obtained by normalizing the",
                "yields of evaporation residues to the elastic",
                "scattering cross section Be-9+Ca-40 at 19-degree as",
                "measured by the monitor detector.",
                "The relative normalization error is of the order of 4%",
                "while the error in absolute normalization is of the",
                "order of 20% .",
                "*By authors*.The measured fusion cross section was",
                "lower than that determined for system and also much",
                "lower than the total reaction cross section calculated",
                "using optical model parameters which fitted elastic",
                "scattering cross sections in the same energy range."
              ]
            }
          ],
